Autenticacion

Up 
post /api/auth/refreshtoken
Obtener un token de acceso para autorizar el acceso a las Apis usando el token de refresco. (refreshtoken)

Consumes

This API call consumes the following media types via the Content-Type request header:
  • application/json

Request body

body TokenRefreshRequest (required)
Body Parameter —

Return type

TokenRefreshResponse

Example data

Content-Type: application/json
{
  "accessToken" : {
    "expiresIn" : 0,
    "token" : "token"
  }
}

Produces

This API call produces the following media types according to the Accept request header; the media type will be conveyed by the Content-Type response header.
  • */*

Responses

200

OK TokenRefreshResponse
Up 
post /api/auth/token
Obtener tokens para autorizar el acceso a las Apis. (token)

Consumes

This API call consumes the following media types via the Content-Type request header:
  • application/json

Request body

body LoginRequest (required)
Body Parameter —

Return type

LoginResponse

Example data

Content-Type: application/json
{
  "role" : "role",
  "id" : "046b6c7f-0b8a-43b9-b35d-6489e6daee91",
  "accessToken" : {
    "expiresIn" : 0,
    "token" : "token"
  },
  "username" : "username"
}

Produces

This API call produces the following media types according to the Accept request header; the media type will be conveyed by the Content-Type response header.
  • */*

Responses

200

OK LoginResponse

Obtener informacion de las recepciones de pago. (getRecepcionPago)

Query parameters

idRecepcionPago (optional)
Query Parameter — format: int64

Return type

array[RecepcionPago]

Example data

Content-Type: application/json
[ {
  "creadoPor" : "creadoPor",
  "fechaCreado" : "05-12-2022 13:16:08",
  "estado" : "ACTIVO",
  "fechaModificado" : "05-12-2022 13:16:08",
  "modificadoPor" : "modificadoPor",
  "id" : 0,
  "nombre" : "nombre"
}, {
  "creadoPor" : "creadoPor",
  "fechaCreado" : "05-12-2022 13:16:08",
  "estado" : "ACTIVO",
  "fechaModificado" : "05-12-2022 13:16:08",
  "modificadoPor" : "modificadoPor",
  "id" : 0,
  "nombre" : "nombre"
} ]

Produces

This API call produces the following media types according to the Accept request header; the media type will be conveyed by the Content-Type response header.
  • */*

Responses

200

OK
